{
  "texts": [
    "The recall of missing answers when the correct response is \"None of the above,\" as shown in Fig. 3, indicates that models struggle more with this option compared to others.",
    "The Yi 1.5 9B model, which had the lowest overall accuracy, achieved the highest score on this specific metric.",
    "This can be attributed to the model selecting \"None of the above\" 520 times, or 37.9% of the questions, leading to an inflated score in this area but poor performance on other metrics.",
    "A similar but less pronounced trend was observed with the Meerkat 7B model, which chose \"None of the above\" 295 times.",
    "Conversely, the Llama 3 8B model almost never selected this option, while the Mistral 7B and Internist 7B models never did."
  ]
}